long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: RFQscrapy is a Chrome extension developed by CodeWithRafiq.com that provides a seamless and secure way to scrape data from any website. This user-friendly tool ensures complete privacy by not storing user data on servers. With RFQscrapy, you can effortlessly scrape data and download it directly as a CSV file. Best of all, it is entirely free to use, with no subscription fees or hidden costs, making it a reliable and cost-effective solution for all your data scraping needs.
